data.description: Four bedroom PLUS den/office situated on large private lot with view fence to green park area in GATED Cielo Noche. Enter through iron gate into courtyard with fountain, then you are greeted by open floor plan (in document tab) with expansive great room & kitchen with huge island & abundant cabinetry. Neutral colors throughout, beautifully maintained by original owners. Huge master bedroom enjoys view to backyard with that private and open view beyond. Ceiling fans throughout, surround sound speakers, window blinds, washer/dryer & frig included. Pavers in courtyard, side walkway, patio & sitting areas. Plenty of room for your pool! Three car tandem garage; 2,645' single story home on 8,773' lot.
